\ \ \ \ createCoord(<svcname>,<dbpath>,[config])
\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \-\ Create\ a\ coord\ node\ in\ target\ host\ of\ sdbcm.
